.env.local

This file is for environment variables that should not be committed to GitHub.

The public URL of your site (useful for metadata/SEO)

NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000

--- Chatbot Configuration ---

Add your API key here.

Note: Prefix with NEXT_PUBLIC_ to make it available to the browser/client-side code.

NEXT_PUBLIC_CHATBOT_API_KEY=AIzaSyDnKEyyREC06wg03YqooMVXwuJcz8yoC_M

--- Future Additions (Examples) ---

If you add Google Analytics later:

NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

If you add a contact form using a service like Resend or SendGrid:

EMAIL_API_KEY=re_123456789